Technology Crowd Funding \\\" width=\\\"410\\\" height=\\\"273\\\" />According to WordSpy.com, the earliest recorded use of the word \\\"crowdfunding\\\" was by Michael Sullivan in fundavlog[5] in August 2006.[6] Crowdfunding as a concept pre-dates the internet and projects like the Statue of Liberty raised funds from a large number of donors. Crowdfunding gained traction after the launch of ArtistShare, in 2003.[7][8][9] Following ArtistShare, more crowdfunding sites started to appear on the web such as EquityNet (2005).\";s:17:\"ign_product_video\";s:130:\"<iframe width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/b7savQVim7E\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\";s:17:\"ign_product_title\";s:6:\"Silver\";s:17:\"ign_product_price\";s:6:\"100.00\";s:29:\"ign_product_short_description\";s:34:\"Support the CityTech CrowdFunding \";s:19:\"ign_product_details\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"ign_product_limit\";s:0:\"\";s:27:\"ign_projectmeta_level_order\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"level-count\";s:1:\"6\";s:6:\"levels\";a:5:{i:2;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:4:\"Gold\";s:5:\"price\";s:6:\"500.00\";s:5:\"limit\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"order\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:41:\"Help the school to support other projects\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Rhodium \";s:5:\"price\";s:7:\"1000.00\";s:5:\"limit\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"order\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:29:\"Be part of something Awesome \";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Platinum \";s:5:\"price\";s:7:\"5000.00\";s:5:\"limit\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"order\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:29:\"Let\\\'s build a better future \";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Lutetium \";s:5:\"price\";s:8:\"10000.00\";s:5:\"limit\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"order\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:127:\"\\\"If your actions inspire others to dream more, learn more, do more and become more, you are a leader.\\\"\r\nJohn Quincy Adams\r\n\r\n\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Citytech Fun\";s:5:\"price\";s:9:\"15,000.00\";s:5:\"limit\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"order\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:17:\"this is citytech \";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}}s:18:\"ign_product_image2\";s:68:\"http://52.3.44.99/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/programming-300x176.jpg\";s:18:\"ign_product_image3\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"ign_product_image4\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"ign_faqs\";s:755:\"Is my contribution tax-deductible?\r\n\r\nYes! All gifts received through this platform are considered donations to Cornell University and are thus tax-deductible. Donors will receive a tax receipt following gift processing.\r\n\r\nWhen will my credit card be charged?\r\n\r\nYour credit card is charged immediately upon finalizing your gift on the site.\r\n\r\nWhere is my donation going?\r\n\r\nIf the project you support is fully funded, 100% of your donation will go directly to the project. There are no deductions of processing or overhead fees.\r\n\r\nIs my contribution tax-deductible?\r\n\r\nYes! All gifts received through this platform are considered donations to Cornell University and are thus tax-deductible. Donors will receive a tax receipt following gift processing.\";s:11:\"ign_updates\";s:811:\"Two Weeks Left!\r\nUpdate (#1)\r\n\r\nHi everyone!\r\n\r\nThanks to everyone that has donated, we have reached 36% of our goal so far. We have two weeks left in our crowdfunding campaign, and we appreciate all of the help that you have given us! Here is a brief update of what we\\\'ve been up to for the past week.\r\n\r\nIn the drylab, we have finalized our design of the treatment applicator: a model of the design is attached to this update. The tip of the applicator is shown in white, and acts as a refillable medication administration port for our treatment, which is represented here as a purple gel. This parenteral mechanism of treatment administration provides the novel possibility to double as a fish tag and allows for repeated administration of treatments through the applicator.\r\n[project_pledged product=\\\"1\\\"]\";s:13:\"advanced_view\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:17:\"add_comment_nonce\";s:10:\"fee4537ca6\";s:22:\"_ajax_fetch_list_nonce\";s:10:\"49b8443f93\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:4:\"ctcf\";s:20:\"post_author_override\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:2:\"ID\";i:28;s:12:\"post_content\";s:59:\"New York City College of Technology Crowd Funding\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";}\";", "yes");
